                <r3d:remarks>The GEOFON earthquake monitoring system acts as key node for rapid global earthquake information for the European-Mediterranean Seismological Centre (EMSC) and as background centre of many tsunami warning centres in the Indian Ocean and in the Mediterranean. GEOFON is part of the Modular Earth Science Infrastructure (MESI) housed at the GeoForschungsZentrum providing services within the “Permanent networks”, “Data Distribution and Archiving” and “Communications” groups of MESI.
More information about the submission of data can be found at: https://geofon.gfz-potsdam.de/contribute.php</r3d:remarks>
